# Overrides the deep child via `parent.inner` (the extracted alias).
# Because `parent.inner` and `parent.mid.inner` resolve to the same
# instance, the overlay is observable through both aliases ‚Äî `direct`
# reads it via the alias, while `via_mid` and `doubled_mid` reach the
# same instance through `mid`.
design parent

value.inner = 99
